    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bands of tape, webbing, or elasticized fabric arranged in an oblong panel which may be slightly curved over the bustline. Worn to compress the breasts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000030201/National Museum of American History, Dictionary of Costume (n.d.)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Banda de cinta, red, o tejido elástico dispuesta en un panel oblongo, el cual puede esta ligeramente curvado sobre la línea de busto. Se lleva para comprimir el pecho.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een langwerpig inzetstuk, gemaakt van stroken band, weefsel of elastische stof, dat bij de borstlijn licht gebogen kan zijn. Wordt gedragen om de borsten plat te drukken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>做成橢圓形裁片的帶子、網帶或伸縮布料，可能在胸線處有弧形設計，主要功能為將胸部壓平。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
